  "Lagoon Focuses On Applying Latest Injection Molding Techniques To Furniture Application. Products Range From Synthetic Wicker Sofas, Dining Tables, Chairs With Excellent Durability. Its High Quality Had Passed Contract Level Certification Of Furniture Of United States, Eu And Japan. Made Of Nontoxic Eco-Friendly Polypropylene, Eu-Made Color Masterbatch, And Uv Stabilizers, Lagoon Outdoor Series Are Water-Proof, Uv-Resist, Easy To Maintain And Clean. Our Manufacturing Plant In Tijuana, Mexico Was Established In 1989. The Plant Covers 15 Hectares, With 350 Staffs, 5 Assembly Lines, 71 Injection Molding Machines, And 7 Blow Molding Machines. Sufficient Capacity Makes Sure Our Customers Around The World Having Steady And On-Time Delivery.": "_assets/media/c6c345d900070925f4bc6919d00c4fb9.png",
